# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# DealershipAI Production Environment Variables
# Generated from: dealershipai-master-manifest.json
# Last Updated: 2025-11-13
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🚀 Vercel Deployment
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
VERCEL_TOKEN=                    # Personal access token from https://vercel.com/account/tokens
VERCEL_PROJECT_ID=               # Project ID from Vercel project settings
VERCEL_ORG_ID=                   # Organization/Team ID from Vercel team settings
DEPLOY_URL=https://dealershipai.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://dealershipai.com

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🔐 Clerk Authentication
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_...
CLERK_SECRET_KEY=sk_...
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_SIGN_IN_URL=/sign-in
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_SIGN_UP_URL=/sign-up
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_AFTER_SIGN_IN_URL=/onboarding
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_AFTER_SIGN_UP_URL=/onboarding

# Clerk domains
CLERK_DOMAIN=clerk.dealershipai.com

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🗄️ Database
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://...           # PostgreSQL connection string
DIRECT_URL=postgresql://...             # Direct connection (for migrations)

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🗺️ Google Maps API (for nearby-dealer route)
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GMAPS_KEY=                              # Google Maps API key
NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_MAPS_KEY=            # Public key for client-side maps

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🗺️ Mapbox (optional - for future map features)
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_MAPBOX_KEY=                 # Mapbox access token
MAPBOX_STYLE_URL=                       # Custom Mapbox style URL

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 💳 Stripe (for payments)
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_...
NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_...
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_...

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 📧 SendGrid (for email notifications)
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
SENDGRID_API_KEY=SG...
SENDGRID_FROM_EMAIL=noreply@dealershipai.com

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🔔 Slack Notifications
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
SLACK_WEBHOOK_URL=https://hooks.slack.com/services/...

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🗄️ Redis/Upstash (for caching)
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=https://...upstash.io
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=...
KV_URL=                                 # Alternative Redis URL
REDIS_URL=                              # Fallback Redis URL

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🤖 AI Services (OpenAI/Anthropic)
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...                   # For GPT-4 and embeddings
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...            # For Claude (optional)

# Model overrides (optional)
AIM_GPT_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini               # AIM GPT valuation model
PULSE_ENGINE_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini          # Pulse Engine narrative model
SCHEMA_ENGINE_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini         # Schema Engineer auto-fix model

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 📊 Analytics & Monitoring
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=G-...     # Google Analytics 4
VERCEL_ANALYTICS_ID=...                 # Vercel Analytics

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🔒 Security & Cron
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
CRON_SECRET=                            # Generate with: openssl rand -base64 32
WEBHOOK_SECRET=                         # For webhook verification

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🎯 Pulse Task Configuration
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PULSE_TASK_BATCH_SIZE=10                # Batch size for task processing
PULSE_RETRY_ATTEMPTS=3                  # Self-healing retry count
PULSE_DEBUG=false                       # Enable verbose logging

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🌐 Supabase (if used)
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://...supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJ...
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJ...

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🔧 Next.js Configuration
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_TELEMETRY_DISABLED=1               # Disable Next.js telemetry
NODE_ENV=production

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 📝 Notes
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Copy this file to .env.local for local development
# 2. Set production values in Vercel project settings
# 3. Never commit .env.local to version control
# 4. Use Vercel CLI to sync: vercel env pull .env.local
# 5. For GitHub Actions, set secrets in repository settings
#
# Required GitHub Secrets:
#   - VERCEL_TOKEN
#   - VERCEL_PROJECT_ID
#   - VERCEL_ORG_ID
#   - SLACK_WEBHOOK_URL
#
# Optional but recommended:
#   - GMAPS_KEY (for geo features)
#   - OPENAI_API_KEY (for AI features)
#   - SENDGRID_API_KEY (for email)
#
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
